  • Light and Intense Daily Conditioner

  • Detangles Instantly and Tame Unruly Hair and Dry Ends
  • Right Balance of Re-hydration for Normal to Naturally Dry Hair
  • Keeps Hair Shiny and Health

The bonacure series comes with a spray conditioner to balance the moisture level of your hair. The innovative spray on function helps you take conditioning for your hair along with you minus a shower.

A Light and Intense Daily Conditioner
The conditioner is not a thick creamy base that leaves behind a residue but one that is light and yet intense to keep your hair conditioned no matter the thickness and length.

Right Balance of Re-hydration for Normal to Naturally Dry Hair
The conditioner suits hair types between normal to naturally dry hair and leaves the strands re-hydrated with an effective result that shows on your soft and silky tresses for longer.

Infuses Hair With Essential Moisture
The spray on conditioner leaves your hair softer with moisture that it needs to fight the damage of pollution and the sun through days at work or college.

Detangles\xa0Instantly and Tames Unruly Hair and Dry Ends
The most common complain of long hair is that it is hard to manage

even dry and frizzy unruly hair.

Keeps Hair Shiny and Healthy
